2026-07-04 20:56:03 [INFO] app.nodes: AIMessage(content="The NVIDIA GeForce RTX 5080 is a high-end graphics processing unit (GPU) from NVIDIA's GeForce 50 series, based on the Blackwell architecture and utilizing the GB203 graphics processor fabricated on a 5 nm process node. It was launched on January 30, 2025.\n\nThe RTX 5080 features 16GB GDDR7 memory, AI-powered DLSS 4, and advanced cooling systems. It is available from various manufacturers such as NVIDIA, ASUS, PNY, and MSI.\n\nSome of the key features of the RTX 5080 include:\n\n*   Blackwell architecture for improved performance\n*   GB203 graphics processor for enhanced gaming capabilities\n*   16GB GDDR7 memory for smooth gameplay\n*   AI-powered DLSS 4 for improved image quality\n*   Advanced cooling systems for reduced noise and heat\n\nThe RTX 5080 is considered one of the best graphics cards in its generation, offering exceptional gaming performance and features. However, it may be prohibitively expensive for some users.\n\nOverall, the NVIDIA GeForce RTX 5080 is a powerful GPU that offers advanced features and improved performance for gamers and content creators.", additional_kwargs={}, response_metadata={'model': 'llama3.1', 'created_at': '2026-07-05T01:56:03.6038056Z', 'done': True, 'done_reason': 'stop', 'total_duration': 2049016200, 'load_duration': 108250500, 'prompt_eval_count': 1755, 'prompt_eval_duration': 254465000, 'eval_count': 241, 'eval_duration': 1675886000, 'logprobs': None, 'model_name': 'llama3.1', 'model_provider': 'ollama'}, id='lc_run--019f2ffd-5d92-7a31-ab63-355135588827-0', tool_calls=[], invalid_tool_calls=[], usage_metadata={'input_tokens': 1755, 'output_tokens': 241, 'total_tokens': 1996})
