2026-07-04 20:56:51 [INFO] app.nodes: AIMessage(content='Clair Obscure is a French role-playing game (RPG) with a mysterious story, puzzles, and exploration using painting and art-related concepts for narration and interaction. The game is part of the Expedition 33 series, which includes a main game and a spinoff called Writers Revenge.\n\nIn Clair Obscure, players can expect to engage in:\n\n1.  **Mysterious Storyline**: The game features a mysterious story that unfolds as players progress through the game.\n2.  **Puzzles and Exploration**: Players will encounter puzzles and challenges that require exploration and interaction with the environment using painting and art-related concepts.\n3.  **Artistic Narration**: The game uses painting and art-related concepts to narrate the story and interact with the environment, adding a unique twist to the traditional RPG experience.\n\nThe spinoff game, Clair Obscure: Writers Revenge, focuses on the lives of the writers and their revenge against the mysterious forces behind the story. This game is also part of the Expedition 33 series and offers a new perspective on the Clair Obscure universe.\n\nOverall, Clair Obscure is an intriguing RPG that combines mystery, puzzles, and artistic narration to create a unique gaming experience.', additional_kwargs={}, response_metadata={'model': 'llama3.1', 'created_at': '2026-07-05T01:56:51.2685332Z', 'done': True, 'done_reason': 'stop', 'total_duration': 1847476400, 'load_duration': 104273600, 'prompt_eval_count': 2235, 'prompt_eval_duration': 36167000, 'eval_count': 247, 'eval_duration': 1703485000, 'logprobs': None, 'model_name': 'llama3.1', 'model_provider': 'ollama'}, id='lc_run--019f2ffe-188c-7093-afa9-f5060c506207-0', tool_calls=[], invalid_tool_calls=[], usage_metadata={'input_tokens': 2235, 'output_tokens': 247, 'total_tokens': 2482})
